<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>

<body>

    <div class="bg-pattern-overlay"></div>

    <header>
        <div class="site-title">
            <img src="/icon.png" alt="Awing Logo" class="header-logo">
            <span>AWING</span>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/origin">Origins</a></li>
                <li><a href="/meals">Meals</a></li>
                <li><a href="/customs">Customs</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>The Cultural Architecture of Awing.</h1>
        <p>A refined repository of historical lineages, sovereign culinary arts, and ancestral laws belonging to the
            Awing Kingdom, situated in the North-West Region of Cameroon.</p>
    </section>

    <main class="container">

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-color-block"></div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <span class="tag">01 / History</span>
                <h2>Origins & Sacred Lineage</h2>
                <p>Explore the deep Tikar migrations, the early foundations of the Santa subdivision fondoms, and
                    the ancient spiritual convenants surrounding the Lake Awing sanctuary.</p>
                <div class="read-more">
                    <a href="/origin" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">View Records &rarr;</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-color-block"></div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <span class="tag">02 / Gastronomy</span>
                <h2>Royal Culinary Arts</h2>
                <p>Discover the precise traditional chemistry of the Achuh yellow soup, limestone pairings, and the
                    complex etiquette of royal banquets.</p>
                <div class="read-more">
                    <a href="/meals" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">View Gallery &rarr;</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-color-block"></div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <span class="tag">03 / Sovereignity</span>
                <h2>Customs & Secret Societies</h2>
                <p>An introduction to the legislative roles of the Nchinda noble circles, palace protocols, and the
                    ancestral steps of the Keleng dance.</p>
                <div class="read-more">
                    <a href="/customs" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">View Customs &rarr;</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy 2026 Awing Cultural Project &bull; Academic Programming Assignment</p>
    </footer>

</body>

</html>